HODONG'S BOOKSHOP

4
00:00:17,226 --> 00:00:23,232
FOURTH BOOK:
<i>HOW TO WIN FRIENDS AND INFLUENCE PEOPLE</i>

5
00:00:25,859 --> 00:00:29,196
The customer who made the reservation
should be here by now.

6
